# Core Lending Modernization – Reference Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR

    subgraph Channels
        A1[Online Banking]
        A2[Mobile App]
        A3[Branch Systems]
    end

    subgraph API_Layer[API Gateway & Façade]
        B1[Lending APIs]
        B2[Origination APIs]
        B3[Servicing APIs]
    end

    subgraph Domain_Services[Domain-Aligned Microservices]
        C1[Loan Origination Service]
        C2[Underwriting Service]
        C3[Fraud & Risk Service]
        C4[Loan Servicing Service]
        C5[Collections Service]
    end

    subgraph Event_Backbone[Event Streaming Platform]
        D1[(Kafka Topics)]
        D2[(Event Schema Registry)]
    end

    subgraph Data_Layer[Data & Coexistence Layer]
        E1[(CDC Engine)]
        E2[(Legacy Core Banking)]
        E3[(Operational Data Store)]
        E4[(Analytics Platform)]
    end

    subgraph Shared_Services[Shared Capabilities]
        F1[Identity & Access]
        F2[Observability]
        F3[NFR & Governance]
    end

    A1 --> B1
    A2 --> B1
    A3 --> B1

    B1 --> C1
    B1 --> C4

    C1 --> D1
    C2 --> D1
    C3 --> D1
    C4 --> D1

    D1 --> C2
    D1 --> C3
    D1 --> C4

    E2 --> E1 --> D1
    D1 --> E3
    D1 --> E4

    C1 --> F2
    C2 --> F2
    C3 --> F2
    C4 --> F2

```
